children.subject: Can the presenters please post slides from this info session? There was not enough room and many of us were unable to see inside from the hallway.

history.content:
There will be a 5th Yr MS info session held at 540 A/B Cory Hall (DOP Center) from 2:00 - 3:00 PM next Tuesday, October 17th. The presentation will be a general overview of the 5th Yr MS program and I'll answer any admissions inquiries afterwards. This info session is meant for 3rd year or 4th year students who are considering the program as an advanced degree.

**Update** 10/17/2017

Access to the slides from today through the link below:

https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B_BcDXsBV1a6Y1oxVW95UnYyQnM

It is a PDF and should also be downloadable.
